org.apache.flex.compiler.tree.mxml

Interface IMXMLMetadataNode

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IASNode, IMXMLNode, ISourceLocation

    public interface IMXMLMetadataNode
extends IMXMLNode
    This AST node represents an MXML <Metadata> tag.

    An IMXMLMetadataNode has N child nodes; each one is an IMetaTagNode representing one metadata declaration inside the tag.
